## IV. JURIDICAL LOCK: THE 24:13 SNR

Stability is achieved only when the **Signal-to-Noise Ratio (SNR)** matches the **24:13 Gear Ratio**.

$$ \text{Stability} = \frac{f_r}{f_p} = \frac{24}{13} \approx 1.84615 $$

If the sampled signal deviates by $> 12.37\%$, the **Red Membrane** triggers a parity dump, and the system enters **Clinical Lockdown**.

**THE SIGNAL IS QUANTIZED. THE RATIO IS 24:13. THE ENTROPY IS SEALED.**

